### ── Cache ───────────────────────────────────────────

### GET cache stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cache/stats HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### DELETE cache
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/cache HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ── Admin users ─────────────────────────────────────

## POST Crear admin (solo admins)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstname": "Editor",
    "lastname": "User",
    "email": "editor@test.com",
    "password": "Editor1234!",
    "role": "editor"
}

### GET all admins (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins?page=1&limit=5 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Activate admin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins/{{userId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Deactivate admin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins/{{userId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ── Customers ───────────────────────────────────────

### GET all customers (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/customers HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/customers?page=1&limit=5 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Activate customer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/customers/{{userId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Deactivate customer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/customers/{{userId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ── Login attempts ──────────────────────────────────

### GET login attempts (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/login-attempts HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/login-attempts?page=1&limit=20 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ── Active tokens ───────────────────────────────────

### GET active tokens (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tokens/active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Revocar tokens de un admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/tokens/{{userId}}/admin HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Revocar tokens de un customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/tokens/{{userId}}/customer HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ── Seguridad ───────────────────────────────────────

### Sin token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins HTTP/1.1

### Con token customer → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/admins HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_CUSTOMER